<plot>Adapted from a Lord Dunsany story,"In the Twilight" is set in 1910. On a beautiful summer's day, a river is crowded with boats. In a moment of carelessness, a man falls overboard. While struggling to reach the surface he strikes his head and sinks to the bottom. In a twilight world, he views past scenes from his life which escalate to a strange and weird climax.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?263575</url></doc>
